                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-979-18400302 t18400302-979-punishment-189"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</hi>
